	<header>
		<a href="/" class="d-flex justify-content-center">
			<img src="../../images/Compass.png" alt="" style="width: 11rem" />
		</a>
	</header>
	<div class="container px-4 py-5" id="custom-cards">
		<p>Nenhum outro usuário tem acesso aos seus posts, essa é uma página visível apenas para você.</p>
		<div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-3 align-items-stretch g-4 py-3">
			<% for(var i=0; i<posts.length; i++) {%>
				<div class="col">
					<div class="card card-cover h-100 text-white rounded-5 shadow-lg"
						style="background-image: url('https://picsum.photos/700/700?random=<%-i%>')">
						<div class="d-flex flex-column h-100 p-5 pb-3 text-white text-shadow-1 text">
							<h2 class="pt-5 mt-5 mb-4 display-6 lh-1">
								<%- posts[i].titulo %>
							</h2>
							<ul class="d-flex list-unstyled mt-auto" style="justify-content: flex-end">
								<li class="d-flex align-items-center me-3">
									<svg class="bi me-2" width="1em" height="1em">
										<use xlink:href="#person" />
									</svg>
									<small>
										<%-posts[i].username %>
									</small>
								</li>
								<li class="d-flex align-items-center me-3">
									<svg class="bi me-2" width="1em" height="1em">
										<use xlink:href="#geo-fill" />
									</svg>
									<small>
										<%- posts[i].pais %>
									</small>
								</li>
								<li class="d-flex align-items-center">
									<svg class="bi me-2" width="1em" height="1em">
										<use xlink:href="#calendar3" />
									</svg>
									<small>2022</small>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<% } %>
		</div>
	</div>


	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
		integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
		crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>

</html>